1979
02:20:04.372 --> 02:20:06.517
We cannot be broken!

1980
02:20:14.257 --> 02:20:16.593
<i>But he knew
that it wasn't enough.</i>

1981
02:20:34.694 --> 02:20:36.505
Great Matriarch.

1982
02:20:36.529 --> 02:20:37.864
wise elders.

1983
02:20:39.699 --> 02:20:41.118
