2062
02:25:32.950 --> 02:25:33.844
Don't look at him.

2063
02:25:33.868 --> 02:25:35.468
He's one step away
from the brig himself.

2064
02:25:35.828 --> 02:25:37.265
Don't tell him
not to look at me.

2065
02:25:37.289 --> 02:25:39.392
What are you gonna do?
Call Daddy?

2066
02:25:39.416 --> 02:25:41.251
