2096
02:27:30.277 --> 02:27:32.005
You keep your post
no matter what happens.

2097
02:27:32.029 --> 02:27:33.030
You read me?

2098
02:27:33.821 --> 02:27:35.032
Lima Charlie. sir.

2099
02:27:41.829 --> 02:27:43.456
If your father and I
do not return.

2100
02:27:44.166 --> 02:27:46.435
