They have IFF badges.

2159
02:34:58.141 --> 02:34:59.202
They're ours.

2160
02:34:59.226 --> 02:35:01.745
Thanks for getting Sully
out in the open. General.

2161
02:35:01.769 --> 02:35:03.230
