2162
02:35:39.932 --> 02:35:41.184
They can't win.

2163
02:35:42.435 --> 02:35:43.728
They're dying.

2164
02:35:45.813 --> 02:35:46.874
Kiri!

2165
02:35:46.898 --> 02:35:48.108
Kiri!

2166
02:35:48.650 --> 02:35:50.693
- Stop her!
- Kiri. Kiri. stop.

2167
02:35:51.444 --> 02:35:52.963
- Kiri.
- Stop. stop. stop. Get back

2168
02:35:52.987 --> 02:35:54.632
